FELASA is a federation of scientific associations focused on laboratory animal science. The governing body is a Board of Management and an Executive Committee.  FELASA is represented by a President. The Executive Committee is elected and all charges are on a volountary basis. FELASA hires an administrative office for accounting and secretary work. &#xd;
More information about the associations integrated in FELASA can be found in this link&#xd;
http://www.felasa.eu/board-of-management
